# Vendored ethos (project-local): vox tracks the identity registry
# (identities/personalities/writing-styles/talents/roles/agents/teams) and the
# durable mission records (missions/ + missions.jsonl). Two things are ignored:
#   1. upstream team-repo dev scaffolding that rode along with the de-submodule
#   2. verbatim per-session activity logs (sessions/**/audit.jsonl) and locks —
#      these are runtime logs (like quarry captures) that must not enter the
#      public repo and would churn the tree on every action.
.punt-labs/ethos/.github/
.punt-labs/ethos/.envrc
.punt-labs/ethos/.biff
.punt-labs/ethos/.gitignore
.punt-labs/ethos/.markdownlint-cli2.jsonc
.punt-labs/ethos/.markdownlint.jsonc
.punt-labs/ethos/.claude/
.punt-labs/ethos/CHANGELOG.md
.punt-labs/ethos/README.md
.punt-labs/ethos/sessions/
.punt-labs/ethos/missions/.create.lock
